<figureCitation box="[159,247,226,252]" captionStart="FIGURES 23 – 30" captionStartId="6.[151,270,868,892]" captionTargetBox="[153,1422,197,842]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,194,847]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 23 – 30. Male genitalia. 23 — Cautires jendeki sp. n.; 24 — Cautires matsudai sp. n.; 25 — Cautires bolavensis sp. n.; 26 — Cautires dembickyi sp. n.; 27 — Cautires hergovitsi sp. n.; 28 — Cautires yunnanus sp. n.; 29 — Cautires kundratai sp. n.; 30 — C. testaceus. Scales 0.5 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/196451/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="37">
